'''梅里德·科里根·麥奎爾'''（'''Mairead Corrigan Maguire '''，{{bd|1944年|1月27日|catIdx=Corrigan}}）是一名[[北爱尔兰|北爱尔兰]]社会活动家。她与[[贝蒂·威廉斯|贝蒂·威廉斯]]一起创立了和平人社团组织，该组织致力于和平解决[[北爱尔兰问题|北爱尔兰问题]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.peacepeople.com/PPHistory.htm |title=Peace People – History |publisher=The Peace People |accessdate=2011-02-20 |quote=This was the beginning of the Movement and the three co-founders worked to harness the energy and desire of many people in Northern Ireland for peace... Ciaran named the movement, Peace People, wrote the Declaration, and set out its rally programme, etc. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110611163252/http://www.peacepeople.com/PPHistory.htm |archive-date=2011-06-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>1977年，两人同获1976年度的[[诺贝尔和平奖|诺贝尔和平奖]]。<ref name=1976PeacePrize>{{cite web |title=The Nobel Peace Prize 1976 |url=http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1976/ |publisher=[[Nobel_Foundation|Nobel Foundation]] |year=2009 |accessdate=2009-07-08 |quote=The Nobel Peace Prize 1976 was awarded jointly to Betty Williams and Mairead Corrigan. Betty Williams and Mairead Corrigan received their Nobel Prize one year later, in 1977. |archive-date=2009-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090714075643/http://nobelprize.org/nobel_prizes/peace/laureates/1976/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>科里根还获得了一些其他奖项。

迈入21世纪后，科里根成为[[以色列|以色列]]对待[[巴勒斯坦|巴勒斯坦]]及[[巴勒斯坦人|巴勒斯坦人]]政策的批评者，她反对对[[加沙|加沙]]的封锁，提倡非暴力的解决巴勒斯坦问题。

